description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Parvati purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 140, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 2 for East, 2 for South, and 2 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40702-12222-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
